# Generated Soroban bindings live in repo — the three stub files
# (`packages/soroban-client/src/bindings/{bridge,factory,wrapper-token}.ts`)
# are committed as a fallback so `pnpm typecheck` is green before contracts
# are deployed.  When `scripts/generate-bindings.ts` is run after
# `pnpm contracts:deploy`, real bindings overwrite the stubs.
